  "text": "Our experimental results showed that the result of our automated algorithm is comparable to the manual definition of the sulci, in that the algorithm-rater error is similar to the rater-rater error. In the absence of a gold standard, we cannot calculate at this point what the absolute accuracy of the algorithm is. However, we can conclude that it can be used to replace laborious manual definition [CITATION_1] , [CITATION_2] . Moreover, we expect that our method will result in more unbiased segmentation, since it is fully automated.",
